[[Dark Trooper/Legends|Dark troopers]] used '''hyperspace capsule''' vehicles when serving the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]], which were were launched from the ''[[Arc Hammer]]''. One devastating feature of the launch pods was the ability to explode on contact with a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] [[Planet/Legends|planet]], which softened the Rebel forces just prior to the [[attack on Tak Base]]. As their name indicated, they had the ability to travel through [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]].

==Behind the scenes==
[[Clint Bajakian]] created the sound effect for the capsule launch, as heard in ''[[Star Wars: Dark Forces|Dark Forces]]''. His sources were the launch sound effect of the [[Viper probe droid]], combined with the sound of a [[Snowspeeder]] (both from [[Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back|''Star Wars:'' Episode V ''The Empire Strikes Back'']]) and his own voice with tweaked frequency, for "a semihuman personality".<ref name="Dark Forces Official Player's Guide">''[[Dark Forces Official Player's Guide]]''</ref>

